ThirdComponentReconstruction - Class in jpiv2
Reconstruction of the third velocity component from a stack of 2d measurements under the assumption of mass-conservation.
ThirdComponentReconstruction(JPiv) - Constructor for class jpiv2.ThirdComponentReconstruction
Creates a new instance of ThirdComponentReconstruction
thirdCompReconDz - Variable in class jpiv2.Settings
Distance between measurement planes (for third component reconstruction based on mass conservation).
thirdCompReconLinReg - Variable in class jpiv2.Settings
The first step of the third component reconstruction is the calculation of the first derivative of the velocity field.
thirdCompReconSkip - Variable in class jpiv2.Settings
Skip measurement planes (for third component reconstruction based on mass conservation).
TIF - Static variable in class jpiv2.FlexFileChooser
